Package org.sbml.jsbml.math.compiler

Class LaTeXCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.util.StringTools
      • org.sbml.jsbml.math.compiler.LaTeXCompiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTNode2Compiler

    public class LaTeXCompiler
extends StringTools
implements ASTNode2Compiler
    Converts ASTNode2Value objects into a LaTeX String to be included into scientific writings or to be displayed in a GUI.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger, Victor Kofia

      • eqBegin

        public static final java.lang.String eqBegin
        Surrounded by new line symbols. Begin equation. This type of equation requires the LaTeX package breqn. It will produce equations with automatic line breaks (LaTeX will compute the optimal place for line breaks). Unfortunately, this does not work for very long denominators.

      • eqEnd

        public static final java.lang.String eqEnd
